GSD.description:
clk: tegra: Fix refcount leak in tegra114_clock_init

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v4.9.331 by commit 1f0e1cbbaffd729560716e9592aa5e609ea93bb6, it was introduced in version v3.10 by commit 2cb5efefd6f7d3e7df9a7430b910a80515821256. For more details please see the references link.
